# Process тАФ Spec-Driven Development

> Full workflow: `PROCESS.md`.

## Spec before code

No implementation without `docs/spec.md` coverage and a `docs/tasks.md` entry.

## Artefact order

```
brainstorm.md тЖТ spec.md тЖТ plan.md тЖТ tasks.md тЖТ implement тЖТ qa-summary.md тЖТ close
```

## Implementation order

```
[TEST] тЖТ FAIL тЖТ implement тЖТ GREEN тЖТ gates тЖТ mark [x]
```

Never mark `[x]` while typecheck or lint is red.

## Commits тАФ Conventional Commits

```
type(scope): description
```

Types: `feat` `fix` `refactor` `docs` `test` `style` `perf` `chore`

Scopes: `client`, `parsers`, `soap`, `config`, `ci`, `docs`

## Branching

- Branch from `main`: `feat/*`, `fix/*`, `chore/*`, `docs/*`
- `main` always green
- Decisions in git artefacts тАФ not chat memory